Text: Cc The pilot RTO Info Database is attached as per your request Please understand that this is a preliminary Draft of the database The database is pretty straightforward The first page contains a listwith links of the current RTO in the database Document links for the talking pointsKey issues have been completed for DStar Florida and Southeastern The others will be completed shortly I welcome any suggestionsconcerns as I will be changing most of the fields of the database on an ongoing basis DH ps If you have problems entering text or making changes the password to unprotect the workbook is Achilles
